info.name: /tremove
info.description: Remove an user or a role from your temporary channel.
examples: /tremove @bieeu - The user `bieeu` will be removed from your channel.
/tremove 919664522267070534 @bieeu - The role of ID `919664522267070534` and `bieeu` will be removed from your channel.
/tremove 919664522267070534 862740130385494027 286166598048284683 @bieeu - All these members will be removed from your channel.
